reviewText: Urban Combat is legit, and extremely effective self-defense hybrid Martial Art. Handed down from Bruce Lee himself' to Dan Insonato, to Emil Martirossian. and now to all the students who learn from Emil are so lucky to learn from such a dedicated Martial Artist and Martial Arts Promoter who is Frank and Practical. Emil Martirossian is an Amazing man and many Martial Artists are likely to aspire to be like him and the great legend "Bruce Lee" himself.
Video qaulity was good but all the techniques were done so fast you coudn`t really see what was happening too rushed for me .Too much showing off
